":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T12:54:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港回歸20年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://booklive.jp/resources/c_media/images/thumb/81/101221_01_1_2L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbooklive.jp%2Fresources%2Fc_media%2Fimages%2Fthumb%2F81%2F101221_01_1_2L.jpg&h=eccffc17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n主權移交後短短數年，英中聯合聲明就變成廢紙！不斷加稅令香港市民的不滿爆發。這導致了十多萬人示威抗議，而中國軍則切斷了電力、燃氣及食水等生命線、封閉啟德機場及對香港進行暴力的軍事封鎖。正當都市生活即將崩潰之際，自稱獨立派的起義武裝佔據了九龍半島一帶繁華地區的酒店群，特種部隊試圖拯救人質，卻反而做成了外國遊客傷亡的慘劇。認為不能袖手旁觀的舊宗主國聯合王國派出艦隊，一邊壓制佔領了仍在建築中的新機場，一邊計算需要提供的補給物資數量，而中國軍則以撒佈水雷對抗。聯合王國強烈要求日本派出掃雷部隊協助。於是，日英開始了大型的空中輸送作戰&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"b1151b8afa9cfe183e245e6b101fa43a66d0259c","tid":338527,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T12:57:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5d808be47a03db3106fb033d96a60ba8cddf480","tid":338527,"uid":67302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T13:02:26.000Z","msg":"黎香港啦"},{"pid":"d101dec1e241b8cfa15aa33a3d1df88a855dddc9","tid":338527,"uid":26671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T13:04:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>英軍隻航母2020先有英軍戰機<br />\n好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2021年先起程黎亞洲<br />\n目前係肯定左艦上會係 RAF 617 Sqn + 某USMC中隊 共24架 F-35B"},{"pid":"82d7d1f79927e077f63cf6f65e88e2e0f82df99d","tid":338527,"uid":42764,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T13:05:39.000Z","msg":"獨立派又再一次幻想假手於人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a43f7fb33e09aec4b8972ec8842bd102624a7f1","tid":338527,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T13:13:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>獨立派又再一次幻想假手於人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 